snippet.title: The Horus Heresy: Legions - Official Titandeath Expansion Trailer
snippet.description:
Titandeath is a new expansion coming to the mobile game The Horus Heresy: Legions, bringing two new playable armies in the form of Loyalist Titans and Traitor Titans, new cards, and more.

#GameTrailers #Gaming
